data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET! Welcome to your affordable piece of St Johns County! Beautifully upgraded 3 bedroom 2 bath secured manufactured home with 8 year old tin roof, 3 year old AC, 4 year old 45 gallon water heater, newer deck in front and brand new composite decking in the back! Gorgeous laminate vinyl plank flooring throughout, 5 year old appliances, and 6 month old luxury master shower! Paver backyard with fire pit and above ground pool for outdoor relaxation and fun! Spacious storage shed conveys. Come check out this magnificent home today!
